@satok16 I am having the same issue on SDK 3.0 and nnlib git v.(721b2d58f). I can compile the make tree VERBOSE=1 V=hexagon_Release_dynamic_toolv72_v60, but on the make tree VERBOSE=1 V=android_Release I ran into the mentioned problem. There is this missing file in the nnlib/Makefile and I changed it as per your comment to add a dummy integer ( I have now both 299 and 224 in it/tensorflow/tensorflow/contrib/hvx/hexagon_controller/src_dummy_data/inception_v3_dummy_int_data.c:

#include <stdint.h>
uint8_t inception_dummy_int_data_299x299[299*299*3] = {};
uint8_t inception_dummy_int_data_224x224[224*224*3] = {};

I passed the error and now have this other compilation error:
